                    Hibernate

        - It is a Java based ORM Tool/Framework
        - Object Relation Mapping


            Java Object                                 Database Table
        Class User                                          table users
         - id                                               id
         - name                                             user_name
         - address                                          user_address

        -- With the help of Hibernate we can map Java class name with Database Table name.
        -- We can map class attributes/fields with table column.
        -- Hibernate will map java datatypes with database datatypes.


        Hibernate is implementation of JPA.

        Java Persistance API-> 
            Standardisation of all the methods to be used for Database operations.


        Hibernate                                   Dapper

        add(User u)                                 save(User u);
        get(id)                                     find(id);
        modify(User u)                              update(u);

            Save()
            find()
            update()


        Interface test{
            void getData();

            int getAmount();
        }

        Class TestImpl implements test{
            // This class have to provide implementation of all the methods of test interface
        }   





                        Compiled
        Java Class  ----------------> ByteCode/Machine Code
                                      (.class)
